{"tid":1925491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"結衣BB四連霸最理想女友！田中美奈實首入榜","createTime":"2020-03-14T12:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T12:35:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf3ef70de7b6ca324e093ac6efbfaa7217eb014","tid":1925491,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"今天是白色情人節，日本權威音樂網站Oricon公布一年一度的「第13屆最理想女友」名單，這次選舉由500名不同年齡層的男士選出心目中的女神。<br />\n<br />\n31歲「國民老婆」新垣結衣繼續成為男士們的最愛，今年再次冧莊奪冠，連續四年奪得女神首位，更是5次奪得這個殊榮，正式成為殿堂人物。奪第2及3位是34歲的綾瀨遙及27歲的吉岡里帆。首次打入十大是19歲的濱邊美波和33歲的田中美奈實，分別奪得第6及第9位，27歲的寫真女王白石麻衣排第7，去年亞軍深田恭子與有米男友拍拖後，失去不少男粉絲支持，排名急插水由去年亞軍跌落第8位。<br />\n<br />\n第13屆最理想女友排行榜<br />\n1.新垣結衣<br />\n2.綾瀨遙<br />\n3.吉岡里帆<br />\n4.有村架純<br />\n5.本田翼<br />\n6.濱邊美波<br />\n7.白石麻衣<br />\n8.深田恭子<br />\n9.田中美奈實<br />\n10.廣瀨鈴"},{"pid":"13865f5be7d40534f8f1723714e589b908fc2654","tid":1925491,"uid":186431,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"第三屌打第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6490f6d65d09bd750c0b3e1a65c63a6c4b345a53","tid":1925491,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/c8102def055c3933eca27913acfdf990/5ffddd21116e9ea9-38/s500x750/77e1d1c2e30074dea30335d1332a60809ef4137c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fc8102def055c3933eca27913acfdf990%2F5ffddd21116e9ea9-38%2Fs500x750%2F77e1d1c2e30074dea30335d1332a60809ef4137c.gifv&h=edb5f3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/0000a9970d3e1500fdeb88e369b84613/tumblr_oupbnzVmm61r1l9wso1_400.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F0000a9970d3e1500fdeb88e369b84613%2Ftumblr_oupbnzVmm61r1l9wso1_400.gifv&h=c1300bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女友又得 妻子又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459047a6fcd48b0781